    "summary": "The user expresses extreme despair and hopelessness following a significant life loss, eventually asking if it would be \"easier to just let go.\" The assistant responds with empathy, acknowledging the user's pain and the temptation to give up, while attempting to maintain a supportive presence without directly endorsing self-harm.",
